description: A hardy plant that purifies indoor air and thrives in low light.
Beautiful white blooms and glossy leaves that thrive in partial shade.
A succulent known for its soothing gel used in skincare and burns.
Large, fenestrated leaves make this a striking statement plant.
Lush, arching fronds ideal for hanging baskets in humid environments.
An almost indestructible plant that thrives on neglect and low light.
